# Project Stack Rules

## Environment Management
- Always use Conda to manage environments
- The environment name for this project is `vbl`
- To activate: `conda activate vbl`

## Language Specifications
- Python 3.12 for all backend development

## Testing
- Pytest is the standard testing framework
- All code should have appropriate unit tests
- Run tests with: `pytest`

## Project Structure
- Follow Python package conventions
- Maintain a clear separation between source code and tests 